# Files Vercel should not include in the build context.
#
# api/ is included automatically (Vercel auto-detects api/*.py as Python
# functions). We only need to exclude things that are NOT needed at deploy
# time but live at the repo root, where Vercel might otherwise mistake them
# for project-level Python code.

# Backend test suites — only needed for local development and CI test runs.
api/test*.py

# Local development artifacts
.venv/
logs/
*.db
*.db-*

# Documentation that bloats the function bundle
docs/
FLASK_API_REFACTORING.md
CLAUDE.md
